message.body: Hi! Come over whenever tonight! Hope this rain stops!
Cool! Maybe after dinner sometime? I will check in cause if it's raining I might not make it. But Im hopefully it will stop!!
Sounds good! I just wanna have a fire!
I think I will head over round 730! What are you having to drink? Also what's your address? It's been awhile since I've been there
We just got to tampopo but should be home soon. I'm gonna get a big beer at the bottle shop you want me to pick you up something?
Should be home by 7:45! I'm glad you are comin!
I also have vodka. Straight vodka shots

Just let me know when you are ready for me! If you are at the bottle shop, there is a six pack of cans that I really like...sly fox pike land pils. If you wanna grab that for me I can bring you some ca$$h
Will do!!! I'll text you when we are almost home!
Ok! I will leave in a few.
